<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - Web: designer / developer / problem solver</title><meta name="description" content="Ed Hatrick-Smith: Who Are You? project "/><meta name="keywords" content="web developer, desginer, photographer, awesome person, solutions"/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">Who Are You? Facebook competition</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / Who Are You? Facebook competition</em></p><article><p class="projects_first"><a href="http://whoareyou.co.nz" target="_blank">Who Are You?</a> are a national organisation set up to promote awareness of sexual assault, as well as provide information to relevant agencies and support networks for victims.</p><p>Their first year was very successful so to help stimulate traffic to the site and their Facebook page they decided to run a Facebook competition. One of their key performance indicators is Facebook "Likes" so it's a good idea.</p><p>I designed the competition based off of previous design collateral we had produced and built the Facebook application itself with <a href="http://www.shortstack.com/" target="_blank">Shortstack</a>. It functions very well and the simple, bold design hopefully cuts through the Facebook clutter.</p><p>The competition is still running so I can't comment on results just yet but it's looking good so far. I'll add the results here once they're in.</p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/whoareyou/image_01_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/whoareyou/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="Who Are You? Facebook competition like"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/whoareyou/image_02_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/whoareyou/image_02_sml.jpg" alt="Who Are You? Facebook competition liked"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div><div class="clearfix"></div></section><ul><li><a href="http://www.facebook.com/WhoAreYou.co.nz/app_148121505341999" target="_blank">Visit Competition</a></li></ul></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>